Short Description:
------------------

   Flying Tigers distributed by HomeBrew Software is a fast
   paced shoot-em up game with multiple weapons, power ups,
   enemies and bosses.  Requires: 386+, 4 Meg RAM as XMS,
   VGA. Adlib(tm)/Soundblaster(tm) optional. (v1.2)  <ASP>


Long Description:
-----------------

   Flying Tigers distributed by HomeBrew Software is a fast
   paced shoot-em up game with multiple weapons, power ups,
   enemies and bosses.  In this episode you will be thrown
   into the middle of 1942, where the techno bosses are
   starting a technology transfer to the Japanese Empire.
   Requires: 386+, 4 Meg RAM as XMS, VGA.  Adlib(tm)/
   Soundblaster(tm) optional. (v1.2)  <ASP>










